cs.CV, cs.IR, cs.MM, cs.DS, cs.NA 

The paper deals with image processing and reconstruction techniques for dual-energy computed tomography. The use of level-set representation and regularization techniques suggests that the paper may belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) or information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-categories. The emphasis on physical properties and the use of numerical methods suggest that the paper may also belong to the numerical analysis (cs.NA) or data structures (cs.DS) sub-categories. Finally, the use of polychromatic dual-energy processing and the focus on image reconstruction suggest that the paper may also belong to the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
